/extras/da7614ee98fd3bb3a9a104a66c242c37.poster.avif?t=1716465585\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/da7614ee98fd3bb3a9a104a66c242c37.webm?t=1716465585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/da7614ee98fd3bb3a9a104a66c242c37.mp4?t=1716465585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rocket Rumble features a simple control scheme so you can hop right into the action! Play your way with either keyboard or controller and control your experience with different gameplay modes! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/4779e45d5920d99a2eb34240a1add798.poster.avif?t=1716465585\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/4779e45d5920d99a2eb34240a1add798.webm?t=1716465585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/4779e45d5920d99a2eb34240a1add798.mp4?t=1716465585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Robots & asteroids and Space Pirates, oh my! Race your way through a ton of different levels with a sci-fi twist! With item drops, boosters, ramps and hazards there's endless fun to discover! Procedurally generated tracks means you'll never have the same race twice! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/7a6c26fedf99f2ebf7af00121437eea2.poster.avif?t=1716465585\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/7a6c26fedf99f2ebf7af00121437eea2.webm?t=1716465585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/7a6c26fedf99f2ebf7af00121437eea2.mp4?t=1716465585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Show off your style with thousands of item combinations! Choose from hats, glasses, badges and more! Plus, stand out from the crowd with tons of suit patterns that are fully customizable from color to size!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/5c8d8610326d8c4f0ce1667ec2050bc2.poster.avif?t=1716465585\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/5c8d8610326d8c4f0ce1667ec2050bc2.webm?t=1716465585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1357430/extras/5c8d8610326d8c4f0ce1667ec2050bc2.mp4?t=1716465585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
